	(text "Note CAN Bus Termination (JP1):\n120Ω termination resistor (R12) between CAN_H and CAN_L.\nJP1 (solder bridge) controls whether the resistor is active.\nClose JP1 if this board is located at the end of the CAN bus.\nLeave JP1 open if board is mid-bus or if bus is already terminated.\nDefault: OPEN (unterminated)\nExactly two 120Ω terminations must be present across entire CAN bus."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
